# 🔐 Caesar Cipher

A simple C++ implementation of the Caesar Cipher encryption algorithm using Object-Oriented Programming (OOP).

## Features

- Encrypt text
- Decrypt text
- Adjustable encryption key
- Supports uppercase and lowercase letters

## Technologies

- C++
- Object-Oriented Programming (OOP)

## How to Compile

```bash
g++ main.cpp -o caesar
```

## Run

```bash
./caesar
```